title: [Empath Guild, Alchemy Supplies]
description: A reflective glass dome roofs over this section of the training annex, admitting the full brightness of the day.  The northern wall of this room, backing on the hallway of the training annex, boasts an expansive display of shelves containing a wonderland of potions, reagents, and materials.  Arcing in a half-moon arrangement around the southern section of the room, the entries to the alchemy workshops beckon.

A reflective glass dome roofs over this section of the training annex, revealing the full splendor of the night sky.  The northern wall of this room, backing on the hallway of the training annex, boasts an expansive display of shelves containing a wonderland of potions, reagents, and materials.  Arcing in a half-moon arrangement around the southern section of the room, the entries to the alchemy workshops beckon.
paths: Obvious exits: northeast, east, southeast, south, southwest, west
